desc.en: DOTA 2 ESL One is back this time from Katowice, Poland. Sixteen teams from across the globe will fight for a part of the $1,000,000 USD prize. The playoffs will be held on February 24-25, 2018 at the Spodek Arena. This is from the Group Stage.

We are bringing together some of the best voices in competitive Heroes of the Storm to entertain you with Heroes of the Storm action from Cologne, Germany. 100.000 US dollars is the prize pool spread between the top four best teams. The participating teams are Team Dignitas, Misfits, Fanatic, ExcelenteEleccion, To Be Determined, The Jabronis, ePunks and GoodlelshetZont.

desc.en: In March 2017, IEM will bring the best gaming action to the Spodek Arena: Heroes of the storm. The gamers will fight for the World Championship title and a prize pool of $100,000 USD. This match-up is the Grand Final between Team Dignitas and Fnatic.
